# Compute GCD of a vec via reduce-style fold.
*gcd(a as i64, b as i64) returns i64
    while b not equals 0
        t is b
        b is a mod b
        a is t
    a

*main
    a is vec(48, 36, 60, 24)
    g is a.get(0)
    i is 1
    while i < a.length
        g is gcd(g, a.get(i))
        i is i + 1
    log g
